From hpages at fhcrc.org  Fri Aug  5 20:30:43 2011
From: hpages at fhcrc.org (=?windows-1252?Q?Herv=E9_Pag=E8s?=)
Date: Fri, 05 Aug 2011 11:30:43 -0700
Subject: [Bioc-devel] New version of rGADEM - ChIP-Seq de novo
