Hi all,

In response to several requests, we have created two RSS feeds: one
indicating new packages added to the devel version of Bioconductor,
and the other showing Subversion commits to trunk (a/k/a the devel
"branch").

There are also web pages which show the same information if you don't
want to use an RSS reader.

The RSS feed URLs are:

http://bioconductor.org/rss/new_packages.rss
http://bioconductor.org/rss/svnlog.rss

The web page URLs are:

http://bioconductor.org/developers/new_packages/
http://bioconductor.org/developers/svnlog/

Both web pages are available from our Developers page
(http://bioconductor.org/developers/).

Please let us know if you have feedback.

Dan


